M||tx|---
M||titl|Preload Based on us Intent
M||impa|md
M||impa|reduces perceived latency
M||tags|bundle, preload, us-intent, hover
M||tx|---
M|Prel|tx|Preload heavy bundles before they're needed to reduce perceived latency.
M|Prel|**Ex|**
M|Prel|tx|```tsx
M|Prel|func|{ onClick: () => void }) {
M|Prel|tx|const preload = () => {
M|Prel|tx|if (typeof window !== 'undefined') {
M|Prel|tx|void import('./monaco-editor')
M|Prel|tx|}
M|Prel|tx|}
M|Prel|tx|return (
M|Prel|tx|<button
M|Prel|tx|onMouseEnter={preload}
M|Prel|tx|onFocus={preload}
M|Prel|tx|onClick={onClick}
M|Prel|tx|>
M|Prel|tx|Open Editor
M|Prel|tx|</button>
M|Prel|tx|)
M|Prel|tx|}
M|Prel|tx|```
M|Prel|**Ex|**
M|Prel|tx|```tsx
M|Prel|func|Props) {
M|Prel|tx|useEffect(() => {
M|Prel|tx|if (flags.editorEnabled && typeof window !== 'undefined') {
M|Prel|tx|void import('./monaco-editor').then(mod => mod.init())
M|Prel|tx|}
M|Prel|tx|}, [flags.editorEnabled])
M|Prel|tx|return <FlagsContext.pr value={flags}>
M|Prel|tx|{children}
M|Prel|tx|</FlagsContext.pr>
M|Prel|tx|}
M|Prel|tx|```
M|Prel|tx|The `typeof window !== 'undefined'` check prevents bundling preloaded modules for SSR, optimizing server bundle size and bd speed.